a=588668&amp;seqTexto=113377&amp;PalavrasDestaque=\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><em>(Inciso acrescido pela Resolu&ccedil;&atilde;o n&ordm; 10, de 2009,</em></span></a></u></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><em> </em></span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><em>e</em></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><em> </em></span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><u><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"http://www2.camara.leg.br/legin/fed/rescad/2013/resolucaodacamaradosdeputados-31-10-julho-2013-776515-publicacaooriginal-140479-pl.html\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><em>revogado pela Resolu&ccedil;&atilde;o n&ordm; 31, de 2013)</em></span></a></u></span></span></p>'),(108,24,NULL,'III - ','<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><u><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"http://www2.camara.gov.br/internet/legislacao/legin.html/textos/visualizarTexto.html?ideNorma=588668&amp;seqTexto=113377&amp;PalavrasDestaque=\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><em>(Inciso acrescido pela Resolu&ccedil;&atilde;o n&ordm; 10, de 2009,</em></span></a></u></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><em> </em></span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><em>e</em></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><em> </em></span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><u><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"http://www2.camara.leg.br/legin/fed/rescad/2013/resolucaodacamaradosdeputados-31-10-julho-2013-776515-publicacaooriginal-140479-pl.html\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><em>revogado pela Resolu&ccedil;&atilde;o n&ordm; 31, de 2013)</em></span></a></u></span></span></p>'),(109,24,NULL,'IV - ','<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><u><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"http://www2.camara.gov.br/internet/legislacao/legin.html/textos/visualizarTexto.html?ideNorma=588668&amp;seqTexto=113377&amp;PalavrasDestaque=\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><em>(Inciso acrescido pela Resolu&ccedil;&atilde;o n&ordm; 10, de 2009,</em></span></a></u></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><em> </em></span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><em>e</em></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><em> </em></span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><u><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"http://www2.camara.leg.br/legin/fed/rescad/2013/resolucaodacamaradosdeputados-31-10-julho-2013-776515-publicacaooriginal-140479-pl.html\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><em>revogado pela Resolu&ccedil;&atilde;o n&ordm; 31, de 2013)</em></span></a></u></span></span></p>'),(110,26,NULL,'I - ','<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">propor medidas destinadas &agrave; preserva&ccedil;&atilde;o e &agrave; promo&ccedil;&atilde;o da imagem e da atua&ccedil;&atilde;o da mulher na C&acirc;mara dos Deputados e no Poder Legislativo;</span></p>'),(111,26,NULL,'II - ','<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">receber, examinar den&uacute;ncias de viol&ecirc;ncia e discrimina&ccedil;&atilde;o contra a mulher e encaminh&aacute;-las aos &oacute;rg&atilde;os competentes;</span></p>'),(112,26,NULL,'III - ','<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">fiscalizar e acompanhar a execu&ccedil;&atilde;o de programas do governo federal que visem &agrave; promo&ccedil;&atilde;o da igualdade de g&ecirc;nero, assim como &agrave; implementa&ccedil;&atilde;o de campanhas educativas e antidiscriminat&oacute;rias de &acirc;mbito nacional;</span></p>'),(113,26,NULL,'IV - ','<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">cooperar com organismos nacionais e internacionais, p&uacute;blicos e privados, voltados &agrave; implementa&ccedil;&atilde;o de pol&iacute;ticas para a mulher;</span></p>'),(114,26,NULL,'V - ','<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">promover pesquisas e estudos sobre direitos da mulher, viol&ecirc;ncia e discrimina&ccedil;&atilde;o contra a mulher, e sobre o d&eacute;fice da sua representa&ccedil;&atilde;o na pol&iacute;tica, inclusive para fins de divulga&ccedil;&atilde;o p&uacute;blica e fornecimento de subs&iacute;dio &agrave;s Comiss&otilde;es da C&acirc;mara dos Deputados;</span></p>'),(115,26,NULL,'VI - ','<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">receber convites e responder a correspond&ecirc;ncias destinadas &agrave; Procuradoria da Mulher;</span></p>'),(116,26,NULL,'VII - ','<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">atender autoridades, no &acirc;mbito da sua compet&ecirc;ncia, especialmente parlamentares mulheres e suas delega&ccedil;&otilde;es nacionais e internacionais, em suas visitas &agrave; C&acirc;mara dos Deputados e tamb&eacute;m encaminhar suas demandas aos &oacute;rg&atilde;os competentes;</span></p>'),(117,26,NULL,'VIII - ','<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">participar, juntamente com a Coordenadoria dos Direitos da Mulher, de solenidades e eventos internos na Casa que envolvam pol&iacute;ticas para a valoriza&ccedil;&atilde;o da mulher;</span></p>'),(118,26,NULL,'IX - ','<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">representar a C&acirc;mara dos Deputados em solenidades e eventos nacionais ou internacionais especificamente destinados &agrave;s pol&iacute;ticas para a valoriza&ccedil;&atilde;o da mulher, mediante designa&ccedil;&atilde;o da Presid&ecirc;ncia da C&acirc;mara. </span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><u><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"http://www2.camara.leg.br/legin/fed/rescad/2013/resolucaodacamaradosdeputados-31-10-julho-2013-776515-publicacaooriginal-140479-pl.html\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><em>(Artigo acrescido pela Resolu&ccedil;&atilde;o n&ordm; 31, de 2013)</em></span></a></u></span></span></p>'),(119,27,NULL,'I - ','<p class=\"western\" style=\"text-align: justify; direction: ltr; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-family: \'Times New Roman\', serif; font-size: 12pt; text-indent: 2cm;\" align=\"justify\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">participar, com os L&iacute;deres, das reuni&otilde;es convocadas